{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_52_03",
  "title": "白石沙季 3話 絶対に、持ち上げるんです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ここは、商売繁盛と学業成就の神社です\n間に合って良かったですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a shrine for business prosperity and academic success.\nI'm glad we made it in time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 7.9666665594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが沢山\n走ってくれたおかげです！　ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s thanks to you\nrunning so much‚ {user}-san! Thank you so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 12.6999998927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは良かったよ……\nまだ朝なのになんだか少し疲れたな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ that's good…\nIt's still morning‚ but I already feel a bit tired…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、休んでいる暇はないですよ\nほら、こっちに来て下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ there's no time to rest.\nCome on‚ over here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2300.0005283,
          "startTime": 24.966667195
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 24.966667195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かった分かった\nん？　このもの凄く大きな石はなんなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright.\nHm? What's this huge stone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7084812634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "この石は、持ち上げることが出来ると\n願いが叶うと言われている霊験あらたかな石なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a sacred stone‚\nsaid to grant your wish if you can lift it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "もの凄く重いらしいので\n持ち上げられる人は限られているのですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's supposed to be incredibly heavy‚\nso only a few people can lift it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1333364049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "私、今日のために腕周りの筋トレを増やして\n来たんです！　隙間時間でのダンベル、腕立て伏せ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I actually increased my arm training just for today—\ndoing dumbbells and push-ups in spare moments…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "クラッピング・プッシュアップなども取り入れて\n私の上腕二頭筋は今最高の状態です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even added clapping push-ups‚\nso my biceps are in the best condition right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 60.4333348791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄く用意周到だな……\nなんでそこまで頑張ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you really prepared thoroughly…\nWhy did you go that far?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 66.2333348791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、決まってます\n千紗が元気で、笑顔でいられますように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ it's obvious.\nSo Chisa can stay healthy and keep smiling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなとずっとアイドルが出来ますように……\n他にも沢山です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So everyone in Moon Tempest can stay idols forever…\nAnd many other things too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0274674187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 78.8000030716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……分かった、俺も星見プロの\nみんなが元気でいられるようにお願いするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Alright‚ then I'll wish for\neveryone at Hoshimi Pro to stay healthy too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 85.733336405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　じゃあ{user}さん\n先に持ち上げてみて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Then‚ {user}-san‚\nPlease try lifting it first!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8000015259,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.668212399995,
          "startTime": 91.2666697383
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 91.2666697383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ、じゃあ…………うぐぐぐぐぐ……！\nな、なんだこれ……びくともしないぞ……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-alright‚ here goes… nghhh…!\nW-what is this… it doesn't move at all…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.4666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺には無理そうだな……予想はしていたが\nここまで来ると少し残念だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like it's impossible for me… I kind of expected that‚\nbut it's still a little disappointing after coming this far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 110.6333348791
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 118.7666681926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "じゃ、じゃあ、私の番ですね。なんだか緊張します……\nとりゃあああああああ～～～～～！　……はあ、はあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-then‚ it's my turn. I'm kind of nervous…\nToryaaaaaaa~~~~~! …hah‚ hah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 121.4333349705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう一回……！\nおりゃああああああああ～～～～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-one more time…!\nOryaaaaaaaa~~~~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 127.4666681926
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 131.8000045975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……びくともしないな……ここは諦めて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It won't move at all… maybe we should give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8000045975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "……嫌です。絶対に、持ち上げるんです！\n持ち上げるまで、東京に帰りませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No. I will absolutely lift it!\nI won't return to Tokyo until I lift it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 145.2000168045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、ぼーっと見てないで{user}さんも\n手伝って下さい！　行きますよ、せーの……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ don't just stand there spacing out‚\nhelp me‚ {user}-san! Here we go‚ ready…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 154.0333501379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "とりゃあああああ～～～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaaahhhhhh—!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0333501379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 158.7000168045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "や、やりました！　持ち上がりました……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-we did it! It lifted…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7000168045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが来てくれて良かったです！\n一人ではご利益をいただくことが出来ませんでしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so glad you were here‚ {user}-san!\nI couldn't have received the blessing alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
